            <title><![CDATA[意大利拒中企旗下公司收购种子生产商]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>意大利政府官员昨天表示，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>该国政府已阻止中国企业所有的先正达集团（Syngenta）</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>收购蔬菜种子生产商Verisem，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>此举强化了意大利总理德拉吉保护关键资产免受不受欢迎外国竞购影</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>响的承诺。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>路透社引述两名直接参与此事的官员说<span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>这一决定是在10月19日的内阁会议上做出的，但尚未公布，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>这是意大利首次否决农业食品行业的收购。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span class="im"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>根据意大利的“黄金力量”法规，政府可以在电信、银行和医疗等被视为具有战略重要性的行业阻止不受欢迎的收购。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1">
        
</div>


</section>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>总部位于瑞士的先正达于2017年被中国化工集团公司以430亿</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>美元（约671亿新元）的价格收购，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>后者今年早些时候并入中化集团。据第三位消息人士透露，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>先正达出价约2亿欧元</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>（约3.12亿新元）<span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>收购Verisem。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span class="im"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>根据Verisem网站信息，这是一家全球种子生产商，在意大利、法国和北美设有加工厂。该公司目前为美国基金Paine Schwarts and Partners所有。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>意大利<span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>农业游说团体Coldiretti呼吁德拉吉阻止先正达的</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>收购，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>称这将让全球蔬菜和草药生产种子控制的战略平衡向亚洲倾斜。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

